claim.claim-text:
1. A biopsy device, comprising:
(a) a body;
(b) a needle extending distally from the body, wherein the needle has a distal end and a lateral aperture positioned proximal to the distal end;
(c) a cutter movable relative to the needle to sever tissue protruding through the lateral aperture, wherein the cutter defines an inner lumen;
(d) a vacuum pump in fluid communication with the lumen of the cutter;
(e) a fluid pump coupled with the body, wherein the fluid pump is in fluid communication with the needle;
(f) a fluid pump actuation assembly in communication with the fluid pump, wherein the fluid pump actuation assembly is operable to actuate the fluid pump to deliver a bolus of fluid to the needle based on movement of the cutter;
(g) a motor operable to actuate the cutter, the vacuum pump, and the fluid pump actuation assembly; and
(h) a first lead screw operable to move the cutter longitudinally relative to the needle.

18. A biopsy device, comprising:
(a) a body;
(b) a needle extending distally from the body, wherein the needle has a distal end and a lateral aperture positioned proximal to the distal end;
(c) a cutter movable relative to the needle to sever tissue protruding through the lateral aperture, wherein the cutter defines an inner lumen;
(d) a fluid pump coupled with the body, wherein the fluid pump is in fluid communication with the needle, wherein the fluid pump comprises a movable member operable to expel fluid from the fluid pump; and
(e) a fluid pump actuation assembly in communication with the fluid pump, wherein the fluid pump actuation assembly comprises a ratcheting member operable to selectively move the movable member of the fluid pump to thereby actuate the fluid pump to deliver a bolus of fluid to the needle based on movement of the cutter, wherein the ratcheting member is: movable proximally in response to proximal movement of the cutter; movable distally in response to distal movement of the cutter; movable proximally relative to the movable member of the fluid pump; and operable to move the movable member of the fluid pump distally to thereby actuate the fluid pump to deliver a bolus of fluid to the needle based on distal movement of the cutter.
